subject: Swimming
Olympic Games (2012)
lead_paragraph: In a surprise victory, American swimmer Nathan Adrian won gold in the men’s 100-meter freestyle. James Magnussen of Australia won silver, and Brent Hayden of Canada earned the bronze medal.
